# Project

- Read `project.yaml` / wrapper at WorkStation `valerie/projects/<name>/` for commands and deploy config
- Per-project naming SSOT: wrapper `memory/naming.md` (platform agent terms stay in WorkStation `shared/glossary.yaml`)
- Tests before push; deploy via WorkStation `scripts/aws/deploy.sh` when `deploy.provider: aws`
- Domain-specific rules belong in this file; generic rules live on WorkStation only
